      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission that slips frequently and an engine that requires a complete overhaul to be roadworthy again. The body shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches, deep scratches, and a cracked windshield. The interior also requires a deep clean and repair of several torn upholstery sections. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or a source for parts.",
