    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minor signs of wear consistent with regular use. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you may find a few small chips or light scratches upon close inspection. Overall, it's a dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
