      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, this car remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a practical, hardworking vehicle that still has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for a daily commuter or a first-time driver!",
