      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this meticulously preserved specimen. Offered in showroom-standard condition, this vehicle boasts a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care and precision maintenance. For the collector or the driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber. We invite you to witness its pristine state firsthand.",
