    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a legacy of pure automotive grace. This car doesn't just sit on the pavement; it commands it with a silhouette that feels sculpted by the wind itself. The deep, lustrous finish catches every glint of the sun, reflecting a life of meticulous care and quiet prestige. Inside, the scent of rich, supple leather invites you to settle into a cabin where time seems to stand still. Every curve of the dash and every note from the exhaust is a testament to an era where driving was an art form. This is more than a vehicle; it is a pristine chapter of history ready to be written by its next custodian.",
